{"tid":1308693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致 政 治 B B 班 嘅 香 港 人","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:47:37.000Z","uid":92836,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"358b2a9c90ec593e27fa95f44cc3652417df3143","tid":1308693,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"咪撚膠化個<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭</span>啦~仆街<br />\n同2014年一樣自斷手腳，學咩人搞抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">連乜閪儂場？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我地5大訴求一樣野都未成功爭取過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">人又死4個，拉又70個</span>（仲慢慢上升）<br />\n點樣對得住佢地嘅犧牲？<br />\n起底組、前線、勇武派、衝立會嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點對得住為左呢場抗爭嘅人？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依加係抗爭呀，唔係加年華呀<br />\n咪撚攞部機出黎影幾下叫抗爭啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n         <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">港豬</span></div>"},{"pid":"fb86dc694a471ee790ab7816b5346f3e56d2229d","tid":1308693,"uid":92836,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，守牆就咁踴躍，企前線就淆底。<br />\n場抗爭失敗咗，好希望香港快啲焦土<br />\n做大灣區共享蝗人榮譽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆你個街，死到臨頭仲<br />\n2014咁玩嘉年華</span>"},{"pid":"cf5f04085f10e5d303acfd51704a31fb258f54e8","tid":1308693,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"仇恨論帶風向分化？"},{"pid":"1421e7fc00a5db9e81bd76953b6333c6e597c569","tid":1308693,"uid":92836,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf5f04085f10e5d303acfd51704a31fb258f54e8","tid":1308693,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"仇恨論帶風向分化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"洗撚分化，根本風向就錯撚曬"},{"pid":"0cf372371347768b4be37ee8f53c9cc91860629c","tid":1308693,"uid":92836,"like":1,"dislike":1,"